上的2篇关于SuperMemo的文章<br>“在 Anki 制作 2.9 万张卡片，复习 33 万次之后，我转用了 SuperMemo“：https:&#47;&#47;zhuanlan.zhihu.com&#47;p&#47;279553703 和 <br>“”同时阅读上百篇文章？渐进阅读之程序员视角(IRAPP)“ https:&#47;&#47;zhuanlan.zhihu.com&#47;p&#47;307996163<br>挺有启发。","like_count":6,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1623019,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/c3/eb/528a1d68.jpg","nickname":"beanSeedling","note":"","ucode":"66C46E399BC191","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":380657,"discussion_content":"“对于某一固定的学科或者领域，学习基本上是个匀加速或者变加速的过程，你的方法会逐渐完善，效率会逐步提高。” —— 模块一底层思维 > 04 ｜ 用科学原理告诉你如何在考场上超长发挥\n-------------------------------------\n看到这个评论的第一眼，其实是想花时间尝试下SuperMemo。但后来反应过来：先尝试不完美但有效的方法，后面再慢慢改善，会对个人提升更有帮助些。\n（“磨刀不误砍柴工”，但今晚的肉还是要先找把刀切了）\n以上仅是个人见解，也感谢层主提供下更新颖的复习工具","likes_number":3,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1624618012,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1351076,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/9d/a4/e481ae48.jpg","nickname":"lesserror","note":"","ucode":"25A54D1165FCF6","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":384107,"discussion_content":"同学，你已经用起来了吗？感觉你说的软件学习成本好大。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1626364897,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":301756,"user_name":"信仰年轻","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1329011,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B2BD881D25FCDD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/47/73/63a3cb41.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625839361,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"18805708545","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"明天前几篇文章就要复习哦","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":301780,"user_name":"Better me","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1261959,"ip_address":"","ucode":"CADF08D357489A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/41/87/46d7e1c2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625880184,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14510782072","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"闭环思维<br>反复复习<br>规律复习","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":298018,"user_name":"Achilles","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1132375,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A4A9711E87C3B6","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/47/57/145622f7.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1623892091,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14508793979","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"什么事闭环？它指的把一件事情从头做到尾巴。拒绝伪勤奋，看一本书需要做笔记，花时间温习，其中的素材和观点需要输出。做试卷需要整理错题集，方便以后重点温习和巩固。整理，复习，应用，尽管琐碎，但是还是很有必要去掉。没有闭环的学习，只会半途而费，浪费时间和精力。复习和学习是齐头并进的事情，先在较近的时间内复习，当你认为记得相对牢固的时候，就可以适当拉长时间。当你稍作努力就可以回想的时候，复习效果更佳。记忆神器 Anki,让你从费心安排每块知识点的复习时间中解放出来。将一本书，化整为零，拆分成各个章节，各个击破，记录到Anki中。两个重要的建议。一是，掌握的不好的知识点可以重新编辑，做一些记录，提现自己下一次复习的关注点在哪里；二是，复习某个章节的时候，针对其中的知识点提出问题，试着主动回想，给出答案。检索式复习比重复阅读的记忆效果要好。","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":314557,"user_name":"三千佛塔烟云下","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2273366,"ip_address":"","ucode":"79B45A1ABD077D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/22/b0/56/d3216fe2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1633223721,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"10223158313","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"必须承认，很多努力是低效的，也许还存在自欺欺人的成分。<br>可以通过&quot;闭环思维&quot;来做到高效学习，学习--输出--复习，真正的player是重视效率的。","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2273366,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/22/b0/56/d3216fe2.jpg","nickname":"三千佛塔烟云下","note":"","ucode":"79B45A1ABD077D","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":400281,"discussion_content":"为学习而学习，做个样子，自然不会在意效率如何了","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1633223812,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":300768,"user_name":"海阔天空","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1551443,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C3711704A3637D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/17/ac/53/ddbe4d80.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625381254,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10215315846","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"学了就忘是客观自然的规律，我们不可能做到学了某项知识，也记住了，然后就能记一辈子，这是不现实的，因为所有人的记忆都符合遗忘曲线的。<br>如果要长期保持对某一些知识的记忆，就需要我们所学的知识形成闭环：学习-检测学习效果-应用-复习-在复习，通过复习不断加强自己的记忆神经链接。<br>复习最佳时机是：我们对所学的知识已经有一定程度的遗忘，但是稍作努力可以大致会想起来的时候。","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":298026,"user_name":"arronK","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1192961,"ip_address":"","ucode":"58DC6FBF2CF0C1","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/34/01/30ca98e6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1623893345,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10213827937","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"要间隔式的检索。而非盯着一个知识点在一个时间段不断重复。<br><br>一定时间的间隔会使得检索的难度更大。但检索的难度越大，对记忆的增强也越有效（具体可以参见存储记忆与提取记忆理论）","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":316016,"user_name":"Terry郑💫","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1112796,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8A032B32396EC3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/fa/dc/d19b01d9.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1634108163,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5929075459","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"知识形成闭环，融会贯通是需要持续重复输入的。把客观的、普世的知识吸收，然后转化成自己的理解，才是高效的复习。方法已经学会了，希望在日后的学习中铭记：温故而知新！","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":301991,"user_name":"信仰年轻","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1329011,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B2BD881D25FCDD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/47/73/63a3cb41.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1626011419,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5920978715","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"06｜教你高效复习：巧用学习神器取得好成绩<br>1、“闭环”：把一件事从头做到尾，学习之余，重视复习和应用，才能实现闭环。<br>简单点：学了不复习，等于没学。<br>2、付出一定的努力去回想知识点，是巩固记忆的必经之路。<br><br>","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":299991,"user_name":"manx00","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1014356,"ip_address":"","ucode":"CA086E73F179E2","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/7a/54/497b1764.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624949195,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5919916491","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"个人总结：<br>学习需要使用闭环的思维，才能减少无效的努力<br>学习之余，还要注重复习和应用才能实现闭环<br>复习效果最好的时候是已经有一定程度遗忘，但能够努力回想起来<br>复习内容太多，可以将内容拆分为，安排每天复习一些<br>复习科目太繁杂，可以使用Anki进行适当的频率复习<br><br>前面章节都是在讲如何学习，这一章讲的是如何让学习变成有效的学习","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":298499,"user_name":"进化菌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1276861,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B30A5F78BB4171","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/7b/bd/ccb37425.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624158714,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":5,"score":"5919126010","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"重视复习和应用能实现学习的闭环。<br>为什么要复习呢？因为人脑在遵循艾宾浩斯遗忘，说白了，就是不被强调的信息会渐渐的遗忘。我们可以通过复习来强调信息的重要性，那么 anki 显然就是这方面的神器啦~","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":356020,"user_name":"LimeSea","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2298863,"ip_address":"广西","ucode":"449CEC